     6→// Purpose:
     7→//     Provides an adapter‐side implementation for scheduled publishing using Quartz.NET.
     8→//     Exposes the domain port IPublishScheduler and an in‐memory fallback in case
     9→//     Quartz cannot be reached (e.g., in unit tests or disconnected execution).
    10→//
    11→// NuGet dependencies (declared in csproj elsewhere):
    12→//     - Quartz (>= 3.4.0)
    13→//     - Microsoft.Extensions.Logging.Abstractions (>= 6.0.0)
